1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 28]

2
00:00:18,526 --> 00:00:19,565
Did you read today's newspaper?

3
00:00:19,926 --> 00:00:21,565
Last night, the mysterious Master He

4
00:00:21,686 --> 00:00:23,285
appeared at the Wu County Chamber of Commerce.

5
00:00:23,526 --> 00:00:24,285
I did!

6
00:00:24,286 --> 00:00:25,765
It's caused a sensation throughout Wu County.

7
00:00:26,126 --> 00:00:27,285
Turns out this Master He

8
00:00:27,286 --> 00:00:28,525
isn't an old man at all,

9
00:00:28,526 --> 00:00:30,525
but the young head of the Zhou family.

10
00:00:33,166 --> 00:00:33,885
His first act

11
00:00:33,886 --> 00:00:35,325
as the new Chamber President

12
00:00:35,526 --> 00:00:36,725
was to rebrand all Zhou family businesses

13
00:00:36,726 --> 00:00:38,165
under the He name.

14
00:00:38,726 --> 00:00:39,165
They say

15
00:00:39,166 --> 00:00:40,765
he invested in our hospital too.

16
00:00:40,766 --> 00:00:42,525
The new advanced medical equipment

17
00:00:42,526 --> 00:00:43,725
was all funded by him.

18
00:00:43,726 --> 00:00:44,685
This way, please.

19
00:00:51,086 --> 00:00:52,165
Isn't that him?

20
00:00:52,646 --> 00:00:53,205
My goodness!

21
00:00:53,366 --> 00:00:55,445
He is so handsome and imposing!

22
00:00:59,926 --> 00:01:01,045
What's he doing here?

23
00:01:02,886 --> 00:01:04,685
I was coerced by Director Zhou

24
00:01:04,686 --> 00:01:06,085
into giving false testimony!

25
00:01:06,246 --> 00:01:07,725
Please don't fire me!

26
00:01:07,726 --> 00:01:08,965
Don't fire me!

27
00:01:08,966 --> 00:01:10,165
Everyone has their struggles.

28
00:01:10,566 --> 00:01:12,285
If I had as much sympathy as others,

29
00:01:12,286 --> 00:01:13,445
I wouldn't be where I am today.

30
00:01:13,926 --> 00:01:14,445
Take him away.

31
00:01:14,446 --> 00:01:15,925
Mr. Zhou!

32
00:01:20,286 --> 00:01:21,085
Zhiqiu!

33
00:01:21,486 --> 00:01:22,605
Please talk to Mr. Zhou for me.

34
00:01:22,606 --> 00:01:23,725
Don't let him fire me!

35
00:01:24,206 --> 00:01:24,925
You're close to him.

36
00:01:25,086 --> 00:01:25,845
He'll believe

37
00:01:26,086 --> 00:01:27,205
whatever you say.

38
00:01:29,446 --> 00:01:31,325
I'm the director of this hospital.

39
00:01:32,206 --> 00:01:33,285
Begging her is pointless.

40
00:01:40,486 --> 00:01:40,965
Ye!

41
00:01:41,286 --> 00:01:42,085
When you were struggling,

42
00:01:42,086 --> 00:01:44,285
I gave you a lifeline!

43
00:01:44,446 --> 00:01:45,365
Got you into this hospital!

44
00:01:45,446 --> 00:01:46,565
Gave you this job!

45
00:01:47,326 --> 00:01:48,165
I beg you!

46
00:01:48,526 --> 00:01:49,725
Who do you think you are?

47
00:01:51,166 --> 00:01:52,445
As if you deserve that title!

48
00:01:53,886 --> 00:01:55,365
Dr. Ye trained for years.

49
00:01:56,126 --> 00:01:57,725
She has professional skills to support herself.

50
00:01:58,526 --> 00:02:00,645
Yet you call it charity?

51
00:02:01,086 --> 00:02:03,365
You made her work the most night shifts

52
00:02:03,526 --> 00:02:05,165
with back-to-back surgeries,

53
00:02:05,446 --> 00:02:06,805
never paying overtime.

54
00:02:07,286 --> 00:02:09,005
And you expect gratitude?

55
00:02:10,246 --> 00:02:10,885
Take him away.

56
00:02:11,446 --> 00:02:12,165
Mr. Zhou!

57
00:02:12,166 --> 00:02:12,925
You can't do this!

58
00:02:13,126 --> 00:02:13,765
Mr. Zhou!

59
00:02:14,046 --> 00:02:14,965
Mr. Zhou!

60
00:02:18,526 --> 00:02:19,205
Everyone,

61
00:02:20,326 --> 00:02:21,925
I have an announcement to make.

62
00:02:23,126 --> 00:02:24,085
Zhongshan Hospital

63
00:02:24,326 --> 00:02:25,525
will soon be renamed

64
00:02:25,526 --> 00:02:26,805
Zhongshan Women and Children's Hospital.

65
00:02:27,486 --> 00:02:28,765
We'll dedicate ourselves to

66
00:02:28,926 --> 00:02:29,725
supporting and training

67
00:02:29,726 --> 00:02:32,045
more female medical professionals

68
00:02:32,366 --> 00:02:34,245
and pediatric scholars.

69
00:02:34,886 --> 00:02:36,445
I hope everyone can join this mission.

70
00:02:38,486 --> 00:02:39,525
My dream for the future

71
00:02:40,086 --> 00:02:43,365
is to open a women's and children's hospital.

72
00:02:43,886 --> 00:02:45,085
To help as many women

73
00:02:45,086 --> 00:02:46,525
and children get medical care as possible,

74
00:02:46,886 --> 00:02:48,205
to help more women

75
00:02:48,206 --> 00:02:49,125
give birth safely

76
00:02:49,126 --> 00:02:50,525
in a secure environment

77
00:02:50,566 --> 00:02:51,805
with proper safeguards,

78
00:02:52,326 --> 00:02:54,245
free from harmful traditional beliefs.

79
00:03:07,286 --> 00:03:08,045
Dr. Ye?

80
00:03:13,646 --> 00:03:14,925
Dr. Ye, are you listening?

81
00:03:17,766 --> 00:03:19,605
Would you be willing to serve as

82
00:03:19,606 --> 00:03:20,885
acting director?

83
00:03:23,886 --> 00:03:25,045
This is wonderful news.

84
00:03:25,046 --> 00:03:25,525
Yes, absolutely.

85
00:03:25,606 --> 00:03:26,245
Me?

86
00:03:31,566 --> 00:03:32,605
I accept.

87
00:03:34,406 --> 00:03:35,525
Of course I accept.

88
00:03:36,406 --> 00:03:37,445
I wholeheartedly accept.

89
00:03:42,886 --> 00:03:43,845
That's fantastic!

90
00:03:49,366 --> 00:03:50,725
In Western hospitals today,

91
00:03:52,046 --> 00:03:53,325
male doctors dominate.

92
00:03:54,766 --> 00:03:56,045
Many women,

93
00:03:56,926 --> 00:03:58,205
even pregnant ones,

94
00:03:59,126 --> 00:04:00,805
feel too embarrassed to seek medical care.

95
00:04:02,366 --> 00:04:02,845
In the future,

96
00:04:03,526 --> 00:04:05,245
with a dedicated women's and children's hospital,

97
00:04:06,246 --> 00:04:07,245
I believe

98
00:04:08,086 --> 00:04:09,605
more and more women

99
00:04:10,526 --> 00:04:12,325
will pursue medical careers.

100
00:04:13,246 --> 00:04:14,805
More women

101
00:04:15,406 --> 00:04:16,805
will seek hospital treatment.

102
00:04:17,886 --> 00:04:19,365
More pregnant women

103
00:04:20,086 --> 00:04:20,605
can choose

104
00:04:20,606 --> 00:04:22,245
scientific childbirth methods.

105
00:04:23,686 --> 00:04:25,125
More children

106
00:04:25,606 --> 00:04:26,685
will receive

107
00:04:26,806 --> 00:04:29,165
specialized pediatric care distinct from adult treatment,

108
00:04:32,846 --> 00:04:34,605
reducing preventable mortality.

109
00:04:35,166 --> 00:04:36,125
This is truly wonderful.

110
00:04:36,126 --> 00:04:37,165
Yes.

111
00:04:38,486 --> 00:04:39,365
Wonderful.

112
00:05:15,166 --> 00:05:16,845
Did you read my old diaries

113
00:05:17,806 --> 00:05:19,725
before deciding to establish this hospital?

114
00:05:20,606 --> 00:05:21,605
Not entirely.

115
00:05:22,926 --> 00:05:23,925
I'm a businessman at heart.

116
00:05:25,806 --> 00:05:26,925
A women's and children's hospital

117
00:05:27,246 --> 00:05:29,045
holds commercial promise and opportunities.

118
00:05:29,686 --> 00:05:30,285
At the same time,

119
00:05:30,606 --> 00:05:31,405
for me,

120
00:05:31,926 --> 00:05:33,485
this is profoundly meaningful.

121
00:05:35,486 --> 00:05:37,085
Then why choose me as director?

122
00:05:38,166 --> 00:05:39,285
Because you're the hospital's

123
00:05:39,286 --> 00:05:40,405
only female doctor.

124
00:05:41,366 --> 00:05:42,285
You understand women's

125
00:05:42,486 --> 00:05:43,685
struggles and hardships

126
00:05:43,686 --> 00:05:45,605
in this environment better than anyone.

127
00:05:47,406 --> 00:05:49,365
Whether training female medical staff

128
00:05:49,926 --> 00:05:50,725
or

129
00:05:51,086 --> 00:05:52,285
empathizing with female patients,

130
00:05:52,926 --> 00:05:54,365
you're the ideal candidate.

131
00:05:59,846 --> 00:06:00,645
Mr. Zhou,

132
00:06:01,526 --> 00:06:02,725
you truly have vision.

133
00:06:03,366 --> 00:06:03,925
Naturally,

134
00:06:04,806 --> 00:06:06,325
you'll face management pressures.

135
00:06:09,926 --> 00:06:10,965
But what if

136
00:06:12,046 --> 00:06:13,325
I perform poorly?

137
00:06:16,766 --> 00:06:18,285
Poor performance...

138
00:06:20,686 --> 00:06:21,565
would mean I punish you

139
00:06:21,806 --> 00:06:22,685
by marrying me.

140
00:06:23,766 --> 00:06:24,925
I've waited long enough.

141
00:06:35,166 --> 00:06:36,045
And what if

142
00:06:38,046 --> 00:06:39,045
I perform exceptionally well?

143
00:06:44,086 --> 00:06:45,645
Exceptional performance...

144
00:06:48,486 --> 00:06:49,285
means I'll bring

145
00:06:49,526 --> 00:06:51,205
all my assets as a live-in son-in-law.

146
00:06:51,526 --> 00:06:52,285
How's that?

147
00:06:54,806 --> 00:06:55,525
Zhou Yimo!

148
00:06:56,686 --> 00:06:58,005
You can't play dirty like this!

149
00:07:06,886 --> 00:07:07,925
I'm not being unreasonable.

150
00:07:10,286 --> 00:07:11,405
In English, "to marry"

151
00:07:11,526 --> 00:07:12,285
and "to wed"

152
00:07:14,046 --> 00:07:15,005
both mean "to marry."

153
00:07:16,686 --> 00:07:18,285
As long as my final destination is you,

154
00:07:19,526 --> 00:07:20,485
I'm fine with either.

155
00:07:27,046 --> 00:07:28,405
You never answer me.

156
00:07:31,046 --> 00:07:32,805
Are you afraid to make me a promise?

157
00:07:41,686 --> 00:07:42,405
Forget it.

158
00:07:42,566 --> 00:07:43,405
I won't pressure you.

159
00:07:44,366 --> 00:07:45,565
As long as you're happy.

160
00:07:57,166 --> 00:07:58,365
"The long wind brings snow,

161
00:08:01,606 --> 00:08:03,045
Sharing white hair with you."

162
00:08:05,246 --> 00:08:05,605
This is

163
00:08:07,606 --> 00:08:09,045
my promise to you.

164
00:08:19,526 --> 00:08:20,365
You can't regret it.

165
00:08:21,166 --> 00:08:21,765
No takebacks.

166
00:08:26,806 --> 00:08:28,045
Deal.

167
00:08:52,806 --> 00:08:53,365
Ms. Ye.

168
00:08:53,806 --> 00:08:55,605
These were all carefully chosen for you by the Master.

169
00:08:55,806 --> 00:08:57,605
They're the finest fabrics available.

170
00:09:20,526 --> 00:09:22,485
This wedding dress has a nice style,

171
00:09:22,926 --> 00:09:23,765
but

172
00:09:23,926 --> 00:09:25,525
it seems a bit small.

173
00:09:27,806 --> 00:09:28,485
Miss,

174
00:09:29,206 --> 00:09:29,925
why aren't you speaking?

175
00:09:36,206 --> 00:09:37,445
Why is it you?

176
00:09:39,526 --> 00:09:40,685
You look truly beautiful

177
00:09:40,806 --> 00:09:41,605
in a wedding dress.

178
00:09:44,806 --> 00:09:45,965
Zhou Yimo and

179
00:09:47,686 --> 00:09:48,605
are getting married soon.

180
00:09:49,326 --> 00:09:50,245
But it hasn't happened yet,

181
00:09:50,846 --> 00:09:51,765
has it?

182
00:09:54,366 --> 00:09:55,685
Zhou Yimo will be here soon.

183
00:09:57,326 --> 00:09:59,045
It's not appropriate for you to be here now.

184
00:10:05,086 --> 00:10:06,125
What do you want?

185
00:10:08,926 --> 00:10:10,485
This is the jade necklace I bought

186
00:10:11,526 --> 00:10:12,685
for a hundred thousand silver dollars

187
00:10:14,086 --> 00:10:15,485
at Jinghu Auction House.

188
00:10:16,486 --> 00:10:17,525
When I first saw it,

189
00:10:17,526 --> 00:10:18,925
I knew it was perfect for you.

190
00:10:21,726 --> 00:10:22,485
But

191
00:10:24,366 --> 00:10:26,205
I didn't know how to give it to you.

192
00:10:30,686 --> 00:10:31,725
Now seeing it on you,

193
00:10:33,726 --> 00:10:34,885
it truly matches.

194
00:10:36,886 --> 00:10:38,205
Since we were kids,

195
00:10:38,926 --> 00:10:40,125
we've always been the perfect match.

196
00:10:41,486 --> 00:10:42,125
When you were little,

197
00:10:44,046 --> 00:10:44,525
you said

198
00:10:45,406 --> 00:10:46,205
when we grew up,

199
00:10:46,646 --> 00:10:47,365
you'd marry me.

200
00:10:49,726 --> 00:10:50,485
Now,

201
00:10:53,126 --> 00:10:54,365
that can finally come true.

202
00:10:58,486 --> 00:11:00,445
That was just childish talk.

203
00:11:01,926 --> 00:11:03,365
How can you take it seriously?

204
00:11:08,086 --> 00:11:08,925
Back then,

205
00:11:10,166 --> 00:11:11,205
you often acted spoiled,

206
00:11:12,206 --> 00:11:13,245
asking me to put up your hair.

207
00:11:14,046 --> 00:11:14,805
Do you remember?

208
00:11:16,926 --> 00:11:17,605
Back then,

209
00:11:18,566 --> 00:11:19,405
we had no money,

210
00:11:20,486 --> 00:11:21,165
no status.

211
00:11:23,366 --> 00:11:24,245
But now,

212
00:11:26,246 --> 00:11:27,445
I have everything.

213
00:11:31,366 --> 00:11:32,165
Yu Shi'an,

214
00:11:34,246 --> 00:11:35,565
we've both grown up.

215
00:11:36,366 --> 00:11:37,525
Marriage in the new era

216
00:11:37,526 --> 00:11:38,725
must be about love,

217
00:11:39,326 --> 00:11:41,245
and even more about responsibility and commitment.

218
00:11:42,406 --> 00:11:44,405
You truly had no money or influence before,

219
00:11:47,486 --> 00:11:48,805
but you were the only person

220
00:11:49,726 --> 00:11:51,125
I trusted in this world.

221
00:11:53,246 --> 00:11:54,245
To be honest,

222
00:11:55,726 --> 00:11:57,845
I did imagine a future with you.

223
00:12:02,406 --> 00:12:03,205
But after you destroyed the autopsy report,

224
00:12:03,206 --> 00:12:04,725
since that day,

225
00:12:06,846 --> 00:12:07,885
between you and me,

226
00:12:10,326 --> 00:12:11,365
there is no possibility.

227
00:12:15,926 --> 00:12:16,725
Officer Yu,

228
00:12:17,486 --> 00:12:18,285
remember this:

229
00:12:18,566 --> 00:12:20,405
the family must be properly consoled,

230
00:12:21,526 --> 00:12:23,245
avoid any incidents.

231
00:12:24,486 --> 00:12:26,525
You know how

232
00:12:26,926 --> 00:12:28,085
the Zhou family operates, right?

233
00:12:54,806 --> 00:12:55,685
Zhou Yimo

234
00:12:56,206 --> 00:12:57,325
intercepted a batch of opium

235
00:12:57,366 --> 00:12:58,565
at the docks last night.

236
00:12:58,886 --> 00:12:59,885
It belonged to Marshal Lu.

237
00:13:00,526 --> 00:13:01,085
Tonight,

238
00:13:01,806 --> 00:13:02,925
he's going to retrieve it.

239
00:13:03,846 --> 00:13:04,805
Tell him to be careful.

240
00:13:07,366 --> 00:13:08,205
It can't be

241
00:13:08,806 --> 00:13:09,725
that there's a bride

242
00:13:11,566 --> 00:13:12,965
but no groom.

243
00:13:37,966 --> 00:13:38,725
How did it go?

244
00:13:39,446 --> 00:13:41,085
The Anti-Opium Committee and local government

245
00:13:41,206 --> 00:13:42,165
have already arrived at the docks,

246
00:13:42,246 --> 00:13:43,565
destroying the opium on-site.

247
00:13:45,486 --> 00:13:46,205
Excellent.

248
00:13:46,806 --> 00:13:48,285
Marshal Lu won't be able to retrieve anything.

249
00:13:48,766 --> 00:13:49,725
By the book,

250
00:13:50,486 --> 00:13:52,245
destroying the opium legitimately,

251
00:13:52,486 --> 00:13:53,565
even if he's angry,

252
00:13:53,726 --> 00:13:55,165
he won't know who to vent on.

253
00:13:56,486 --> 00:13:58,365
All thanks to Yu Shi'an tipping us off.

254
00:13:58,806 --> 00:13:59,685
Otherwise tonight

255
00:13:59,726 --> 00:14:01,205
would've been another bloodbath.

256
00:14:03,486 --> 00:14:04,365
Not us.

257
00:14:05,486 --> 00:14:06,485
He's doing it for you.

258
00:14:09,686 --> 00:14:10,645
You're jealous.

259
00:14:15,126 --> 00:14:16,405
Why would I be jealous?

260
00:14:16,686 --> 00:14:18,285
I'm such a broad-minded man.

261
00:14:20,206 --> 00:14:21,325
From the Chamber of Commerce's perspective,

262
00:14:21,326 --> 00:14:22,365
I should thank him.

263
00:14:24,446 --> 00:14:26,085
As your fiancé,

264
00:14:26,366 --> 00:14:27,725
I trust our relationship.

265
00:14:31,366 --> 00:14:32,205
Not jealous.

266
00:14:34,646 --> 00:14:35,365
Easy now.

267
00:14:36,326 --> 00:14:37,165
What happened?

268
00:14:37,486 --> 00:14:38,845
Yu took men to the docks

269
00:14:38,846 --> 00:14:39,765
looking for Marshal's goods,

270
00:14:39,926 --> 00:14:40,365
but

271
00:14:40,406 --> 00:14:41,005
found nothing.

272
00:14:41,446 --> 00:14:41,925
Shut up!

273
00:14:44,086 --> 00:14:44,885
We're at the hospital.

274
00:14:45,806 --> 00:14:46,685
You all go back first.

275
00:14:47,446 --> 00:14:48,365
Yes, yes.

276
00:15:14,166 --> 00:15:15,365
The wound looks scary,

277
00:15:15,646 --> 00:15:16,765
but it's just superficial.

278
00:15:16,806 --> 00:15:17,845
It'll heal soon.

279
00:15:31,326 --> 00:15:31,925
Lieutenant Yu,

280
00:15:34,366 --> 00:15:35,565
you didn't need to do this.

281
00:15:36,646 --> 00:15:37,565
I didn't think that much.

282
00:15:38,806 --> 00:15:39,685
I just felt

283
00:15:41,686 --> 00:15:43,165
if something happened to Zhou Yimo,

284
00:15:47,446 --> 00:15:48,485
you'd be sad.

285
00:15:49,206 --> 00:15:49,965
Was it worth it?

286
00:15:51,486 --> 00:15:52,845
No question of worth.

287
00:15:56,486 --> 00:15:57,245
I chose to.

288
00:16:04,086 --> 00:16:04,725
Don't move.

289
00:16:06,966 --> 00:16:08,525
Marshal Lu won't let this go.

290
00:16:09,246 --> 00:16:10,645
Tell Zhou Yimo to be careful.

291
00:16:27,806 --> 00:16:28,965
This gift is too valuable.

292
00:16:29,726 --> 00:16:30,525
I can't accept it.

293
00:16:31,766 --> 00:16:32,525
Between us,

294
00:16:32,966 --> 00:16:34,205
should we be this formal?

295
00:16:36,446 --> 00:16:37,725
It's just something I'm giving you

296
00:16:38,246 --> 00:16:39,485
as a wedding gift.

297
00:16:46,966 --> 00:16:48,445
If you insist on refusing,

298
00:16:49,566 --> 00:16:50,365
then

299
00:16:51,486 --> 00:16:52,725
consider it my donation to the hospital.

300
00:16:54,366 --> 00:16:55,365
You can sell it

301
00:16:55,566 --> 00:16:56,525
and use the money for patients

302
00:16:56,526 --> 00:16:57,685
in urgent need at home

303
00:16:58,046 --> 00:16:58,845
as medical expenses.

304
00:17:14,526 --> 00:17:15,285
Is that acceptable,

305
00:17:15,686 --> 00:17:16,485
Director Ye?

306
00:17:30,486 --> 00:17:31,205
Alright,

307
00:17:32,246 --> 00:17:32,965
I'll accept it.

308
00:17:34,446 --> 00:17:35,965
Then I'll thank you on behalf of

309
00:17:36,406 --> 00:17:37,205
our patients,

310
00:17:37,846 --> 00:17:38,645
Lieutenant Yu.

311
00:17:39,686 --> 00:17:40,445
In a few days,

312
00:17:40,526 --> 00:17:41,285
I'll have someone

313
00:17:41,286 --> 00:17:42,325
deliver the donation certificate

314
00:17:42,326 --> 00:17:43,445
to your residence.

315
00:17:46,886 --> 00:17:47,485
Good.

316
00:18:03,526 --> 00:18:04,485
I'll take my leave now.

317
00:18:06,926 --> 00:18:07,845
Take care of your wound.
